            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000000306\">[33]</$link><br>\n[ cf. “Il.” xxiv. 587, 588 where the lines refer to the washing the dead body of Hector.]</p></div></div>"
