            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000000986\">[89]</$link><br>\n[ Brides presented themselves instinctively to the imagination of the writer, as the phase of humanity which she found most interesting.]</p></div></div>"
