        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002083\">[177]</$link><br>\n[ There were a hundred and eight Suitors.]</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p><a></a></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002091\">[178]</$link><br>\n[ Lord Grimthorpe, whose understanding does not lend itself to easy imposition, has been good enough to write to me about my conviction that the “Odyssey” was written by a woman, and to send me remarks upon the gross absurdity of the incident here recorded. It is plain that all the authoress cared about was that the women should be hanged: as for attempting to realise, or to make her readers realise, how the hanging was done, this was of no consequence. The reader must take her word for it and ask no questions. Lord Grimthorpe wrote:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\">“I had better send you my ideas about Nausicaa’s hanging of the maids (not ‘maidens,’ of whom Froude wrote so well in his ‘Science of History’) before I forget it all. Luckily for me Liddell &amp; Scott have specially translated most of the doubtful words, referring to this very place.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\">“A ship’s cable. I don’t know how big a ship she meant, but it must have been a very small one indeed if its ‘cable’ could be used to tie tightly round a woman’s neck, and still more round a dozen of them ‘in a row,’ besides being strong enough to hold them and pull them all up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\">“A dozen average women would need the weight and strength of more than a dozen strong heavy men even over the best pulley hung to the roof over them; and the idea of pulling them up by a rope hung anyhow round a pillar {Greek} is absurdly impossible; and how a dozen of them could be hung dangling round one post is a problem which a senior wrangler would be puzzled to answer... She had better have let Telemachus use his sword as he had intended till she changed his mind for him.”]</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p><a></a></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000002101\">[179]</$link><br>\n[ Then they had all been in Ulysses’ service over twenty years; perhaps the twelve guilty ones had been engaged more recently.]</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/769d3732d4c38307/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-769d3732d4c38307-4b6aff twpub-769d3732d4c38307-39c75b twpub-769d3732d4c38307-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
